<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    It's possible that there was a little resentment on Mrs. Bakers part. Holling was mostly just paranoid I suspect. But it's also seem likely that Mrs. <a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    It's possible that there was a little resentment on Mrs. Bakers part. Holling was mostly just paranoid I suspect. But it's also seem likely that Mrs. Baker looked forward to this time as her free time when half the class went to Temple and the other half went to Catechism. Only Holling was left behind. Recall that Mrs. Baker did try to have him repeat 6th grade math. <a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
