<li class='cover' id='bookCover_11797411'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/11797411-all-the-money-in-the-world"><img alt="All the Money in the World: What the Happiest People Know about Getting and Spending" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1348215241l/11797411._SX98_.jpg" />
